snippet.title: Space Pilgrim Episode IV: Sol - Steam Trailer
snippet.description: Locked away in the most secure prison in the galaxy, with little hope of escape, Gail Pilgrim faces the most difficult ordeals of her life. Her only hope lies in trusting those who she has come to regard as her friends.
